data.description: MOVE IN READY HOME!  This stunning ''Pelican Bay'' Floor Plan Home is highly upgraded throughout.  The home features 3 Bedrooms/2.5 Bathrooms in a split floor plan, plus a separate Den/Office.  The entry features an Iron/Glass door, leading to a formal entry area to the Great Room.  The Great Room features an extensively upgraded Kitchen with a large island, gas cooktop, built in wall oven/microwave, separate walk in pantry and under cabinet lighting. This home features a LARGE 4 Car Tandem Garage. The backyard is complete with a paver patio and artificial turf yard.  The home features a tankless gas water heater, ceiling fanes throughout, Ring Doorbell System, and upgraded lighting fixtures.  All furniture and refrigerator, washer and dryer available for sale on separate bill of sale.
